chemaxon.marvin.sketch

Class SketchParameterConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • chemaxon.marvin.common.ParameterConstants
      • chemaxon.marvin.sketch.SketchParameterConstants

  • public class SketchParameterConstants
extends ParameterConstants
    Parameters of MarvinSketch Applet and Bean.
    The parameters of the JMSketch applet can be set using the <param> HTML tag. The parameters of the MSketchPane JavaBean component can be set using the setParams and setSketchMode method.
    Since:
    Marvin 5.2
    Version:
    5.2.2, 05/04/2009
    Author:
    Eva Hollo, Judit Vasko-Szedlar
